aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
POWER TOWERS from K Kingkang 
The Power Tower is a versatile piece of equipment that offers numerous benefits if used properly. 
Full Body Workouts: We will give you an example full body workout that can be done while only using your body and the Power Tower. The only muscle groups that are difficult to work hard on the Power Tower are legs because you’re suspended in air for the most part. You can perform multiple compound exercises like pull-ups, dips and push-ups on the Power Tower to help stimulate muscle growth. Performing bodyweight exercises will help you to maintain and improve your overall health. The Power Tower allows users to make most exercises either easier or more difficult by incorporating supplemental tools like resistance bands, weights, weighted vests, suspension trainers and more. 
Unique Bend Suction Cups 
This dip stands owns a unique Bend suction cups in the bottom, which can adjust the flatness that contacts with the ground. Made the power tower more Safety and strong stability. 
Pull-up Benefits 
Pull ups are an excellent exercise to get stronger. They work multiple muscle groups simultaneously, which is why they help you build more strength and muscle than other exercises. 
Vertical Knee Raises 
Vertical knee raises are one way to increase core strength, and a strong core helps with everyday movement both inside and outside the gym, from getting out of bed in the morning to lifting a barbell, A strong core also helps with form, increases athleticism, improves posture, protects organs, and reduces your risk of injury. 
Push-up bar benefits 
It's easy to think that push-ups are only good for your chest and arms. But compound exercise engages multiple muscle groups at once. push-ups work your: 
Chest (pectorals) 
Shoulders (deltoids) 
Arms (triceps and biceps) 
Back (latissimus dorsi and erector spinae) 
Stomach (abdominals) 
Hips (gluteals) 
Long-size Base Support 
49.2” Long-size base has more loading points, which makes the power tower more stable 
Comfortable & Durable Leather Pads 
High quality arm and back cushions made of breathable odorless PU Leather, which give users a fully concentrated, comfortable workout without worrying about any unnecessary strain during exercise. 
Adjustable Height Power tower 
The height of this power tower can be adjusted, there are 7 holes location, the adjustable height range is 64.9-88.6 inches. 
Power tower detail size 
The most suitable size, suitable for most people

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
ERGONOMIC HANDLES 
Curved, contoured handles add potential variations to your grip and workouts Ergonomic design aids in comfort when performing assisted squats. 
EXTRA RESISTANCE 
Featuring 4 resistance bands rated at 22 LB each, the Row-N-Ride Plus increases the intensity of your assisted squats and helps to shape your glutes, thighs, and legs. 
PADDED SEAT 
The thick and supple cushioned seat provides just the right amount of support. It supports 4 levels of lateral adjustability and 3 levels of default incline positions. 
DIGITAL MONITOR 
Stay focused on your goals and track your progress with the Digital Monitor which tracks: Calories, Count, Reps/Min, Time and includes a Scan function. 
HIGH MAX WEIGHT 
This foldable squat assist exercise equipment is designed for powerful workouts. A 300 LB max weight gives you the confidence to push for the extra rep and go the distance. 
NON-SLIP FOOT PEDALS 
Its self-leveling pedals help you to get in and out of the bike in a breeze. Stable end caps prevent any movement to ensure you have a stable and safe workout. 
CONVENIENCE 
Easily store almost anywhere in your home. Remove the knob, fold, and store; as easy as 1, 2, 3. 
EXERCISE IDEAS 
MAXIMUM RANGE 
Saddle angle control allows you to adjust the saddle at 30, 60, and 90 degrees giving you deeper squat positions 
BENT OVER ROW 
Single arm upright rows help to strengthen your back and biceps, and can easily be completed by dismounting your Row-N-Ride and pulling up and back on the seat. 
DEADLIFT 
The Row-N-Ride can even be used to complete deadlifts, which are great for targeting the posterior chain muscles like the glutes, hamstrings, calves, and core! 
INCLINE CHEST PRESS 
Challenge your upper chest, shoulders, and core muscles as you press up on the seat of your Row-N-Ride to complete incline chest press.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Check it out! The Panther is the ultimate destination for your home gym journey 
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
Does this machine come with all the bells and whistles, or do I have to buy extra stuff? 
Oh, it’s got all the bells and whistles, my friend. No need to go hunting for extra gear. You’ve got your Smith machine, pec deck, cable pulley system, pull-up bars... it’s a one-stop shop for your entire workout. Just bring your muscles. 
What’s with the 7-degree angled Smith machine? Does that actually make a difference? 
Oh yeah, big time! That 7-degree angle isn’t just for looks—it’s all about smoother, more natural movement. No more “joint grinds” that feel like you’re wrestling with the machine. You’ll feel like you're lifting with the pros. 
Can I actually fit this beast in my garage, or is it gonna need its own room? 
It’s a powerhouse, but we designed it to save space. Think of it like a Transformer—big performance, compact design. It'll fit in your garage or home gym without turning it into a circus tent. 
What’s the deal with the cable ratios? 
No calculators needed! Here's the breakdown: 
4:1 on the pulley system 
2:1 on the pec deck 
1:1 on the low row 
Mix these ratios, and you’ve got versatile training for every muscle, every angle. It’s like having a whole gym in one machine! 
Is the pec deck on this machine really as good as it sounds, or is it just a gimmick? 
Nope, no gimmicks here! The built-in pec deck is smooth, comfy, and hits your chest just right. Adjustable settings let you customize for the perfect stretch and contraction. It's like having a trainer, minus the sweat!

Doorway pull up bars have rightfully earned the respect of fitness enthusiasts. Great workouts at home start with a pull up bar ready to go at a moment's notice. The addition of the elevated bar extends your range of motion for the kind of performance you expect from the mounted bars at the gym.

Perfect Support for Sit Ups

Add optional Ab Straps and Gymnastic Rings to transform your Doorway Pull Up Bar into a complete home gym. Pull up bar accessories expand your favorite exercises with new compound movements and increase your rep counts to full sets with assisted exercise variations. aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer

The patented portable Dip Station with adjustable width to correctly fit you and every member of your family 
The only width adjustable Dip Station 
Angled grips and adjustable width engage the right muscles with proper form. A Dip Station that fits reduces strain on the shoulders, elbows and wrists so you can get the right results in less time. 
Proper width keeps your forearms vertical and positions hands under shoulders 
Angled grips align hands and wrists with your upper arms to reduce strain 
Correct arm and hand position helps keep shoulders down and back so you can access and apply more power 
The Original Dip Bar Fitness Station 
Get effective workouts at home and on the go 
Get Ultimate results, versatility and value with the Dip Bar Fitness Station. Rapidly build chest, shoulders, arms and core with better workouts every day. 
Thick 1.5 inch steel tubing and 3 foot tall frame is suitable for users up to 6'5” and 350 lbs 
Angled grips and adjustable width sets the grips from 19 to 24 inches to provide a proper fit for you and every member of your family 
Open frame and angled grips support proper form for chest and tricep dips, bodyweight rows, and knee raises 
Stylish design enhances the look of your space 
Color coded assembly. Folds for storage with no tools required. Compact frame is ideal for small spaces 
Expandable with Weighted Dip Belt Agility Trainer (sold separately) 
The Dip Bar Fitness Station is supported with our online workout guides, blog, and workout videos 
Rapid Results, Core Strength, Balanced Development, and Assisted Exercise Variation 
The Fit that Promotes Form 
Dips rapidly build a sculpted upper body when supported with good form. Proper position of the shoulders, wrists, and arms reduces strain and engages the right muscles so you can focus on repetition. Width position I at 19” fits most users up to 190lbs and position II at 24" fits users up to 350lbs. 
Build Core Strength 
L-Sits and Knee Raises tone core and strengthen lower back. Adjustable leveling feet and high density foam grips provide stability and comfort for longer workouts. Simple color coded assembly, no tools required! 
Balance Chest and Back with Bodyweight Rows 
Compound Bodyweight exercises deliver the fastest results including full bodyweight rows to balance chest and shoulder development. Innovative design supports up to 350 lbs for users up to 6 feet 5 inches and folds for easy storage. 
Assisted Exercise Variation 
Assisted exercise variations let you easily control resistance for complete full intensity workouts right from day one. Supercharge your metabolism with strength training and interval workouts that get fast effective results. 
Easy Portability and Set-Up 
The Ultimate Body Press Dip Bar Fitness Station is sized for you and your home workout space so you can leave it set up and ready to go. But it's also easy to fold it down after each use for storage under a bed, in the closet, or in the trunk of your car. 
Fast Color Coded Assembly with Quick Release Pins 
The Dip Station ships in four pieces to allow the handles to rotate into a flat position and to enable our patented adjustable width positions. Assembly and disassembly takes just moments with integrated quick release clips and color coded sections. 
Integrated leveling feet adjust for perfect stability 
Integrated leveling feet ensure your Dip Station is always sitting perfectly flat on the floor for optimum stability. Each corner is adjustable with 8 positions to give you total placement flexibility. 
Pro Tip: Ensure maximum stability by positioning the feet at the outer four corners of the base bars. 
Align your Dip Station to Finish your Set-Up 
The Dip Station is engineered for easy disassembly and folding. You will notice a small degree of play in the 4 sections that firms up once your bodyweight is applied. This is to prevent the sections from locking together during use, preventing disassembly. After set-up, ensure that your dip station handles are at the correct angles by aligning the seams at the front and back floor sections as shown in the illustration.

Product Description
Ally Peaks PULL UP ASSISTANCE BANDS SYSTEM 
Experience The Difference 
OUR GOAL: Provide advanced products to improve your life.

We continually work to improve our products and search for the best available materials. We are certain you will be happy with the value of our products. when you receive our products and it is helpful for you. Our greatest goal is that our products will be valuable to you. 
FIVE CHARACTERISTICS OF OUR PULL UP ASSIST BANDS 
REMOVABLE DESIGN 
You can change the resistance band with different tension for training, and can be matched with any other resistance band equipment in your home. 
Military-GRADE NYLON STRAP 
Let the pull up assist band can support up to 700lbs.(ordinary nylon strap only can support up to 300lbs,easily deformed and there is a risk of fracture when used for a long time) 
SMOOTHER AND WIDENED METAL BUCKLE 
All the buttons on the pullup assistant band are made of metal.(In order to cut cost,some ordinary pull up assist band’s part are made of plastic.It is very dangerous when used for a long time) 
100% NATURAL LATAX 
Our pull up assistance bands set are made of 100% natural latex , which makes resistance bands assist up to 410LBS. The resistance bands can remain high elastic after years of training and exercising. 
Note:The resilience of NATURAL LATAX are significantly better than other materials such as TPE.Greatly increase the fitness effect.(In order to cut cost,some resistance bands use TPE material to pass off as latex material.) 
ONE SECOND BECOMES MULTI-FUNCTIONAL TRAINING 
Resistance bands can be used with the door anchor 
Using of the door anchor

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Adjustable Length: 
Easily adjust the band length to suit your height and resistance preferences. Whether you prefer using the band for two feet or knees, the customization ensures an optimal workout. 
• Versatile Attachment: 
• The band can be easily attached to any gym or pull-up bar, providing a convenient workout anytime, anywhere. 
• Portable Design: 
• Comes with a travel carry bag, making it perfect for on-the-go fitness enthusiasts. Take your workout routine with you wherever you go! 
• Build Strength Gradually: 
• Say goodbye to struggling with full weight pull-ups. Our assistance bands help you build strength progressively, allowing you to achieve your fitness goals efficiently. 
Simple and Convenient Installation Guide 
Here’s a step-by-step guide on how to use your pull-up assist band set: 
1. Attach the Webbing: 
• Open the carabiner clip. 
• Attach the webbing to the pull-up bar by securing it with the carabiner clip. 
2. Hang the Foot Rest: 
• Hang the foot rest (sponge pad sling) from the webbing. 
3. Attach the Resistance Bands: 
• Hang the resistance bands onto the D-ring metal buckle on the webbing. 
4. Adjust the Strap Length: 
• Use the steel buckle to adjust the strap to the appropriate length for your height and pull-up routine. 
5. Begin Your Pull-Up Routine: 
• Stand or kneel on the sponge pad sling, depending on your preference and exercise requirements. 
• Begin your pull-up exercises with the assistance of the bands.

features: 【OPTIMIZED MOTION】: Easily sculpt a V-shaped back with our seated row machine! Replicate the traditional pulling movement towards the chest, it's ergonomically designed to follow the body's natural motion, ensuring maximum engagement and a full range of motion. Feel the intensity as your back muscles engage, supported by smooth-operating bearings for a seamless exercise experience. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned pro, mastering this back machine is effortless.

【COMMERCIAL-GRADE MACHINE】: Upgrade to a commercial-grade fitness equipment at an affordable price! With dimensions of 58.2" x 42" x 55.9", our seated row machine plate loaded offers generous space for fluid movement. Crafted from heavy-duty 13-gauge steel, its sturdy frame supports up to 600lbs, guaranteeing stability during rigorous workouts. Plus, its extended 9.6" weight holder effortlessly holds four 35lbs weights. Experience durability, stability, and convenience all in one machine.

【MULTIPLE GRIP HANDLES】: Featuring multiple grip handles that cater to every inch of your back, this leverage seated row machine allows you to effortlessly target various muscle groups with ease.The narrow grips for lats and mid back, while wider grips can target your upper back and delts, you can customize your workout for optimal results. Plus, our non-slip coated handles ensure comfort and safety throughout the workouts.

【INDEPENDENT ARMS】: Back machine’s independent mechanical arms grant you the flexibility to alternate sides or engage both simultaneously. This versatility makes the lat machine particularly advantageous for people aiming to balance unilateral strength. By adjusting the weights, customize your exercises to target specific areas effectively. Moreover, the inclusion of an Assist Handle offers additional support during single-arm exercises, promoting proper form and amplifying your results.

【COMFORT& ADJUSTABILITY】: Boasting an extra-thick seat and chest cushion for optimal comfort during intense sessions. Adjustable in four positions to suit different body types, the back row machine seamlessly transitions to a standing row with a quick-detach seat, maximizing muscle engagement. Non-slip foot pedals ensure stability and effective upper body isolation. Experience the pinnacle of seated rowing, where comfort, adjustability, and performance converge effortlessly.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Marcy Power Cage System 
The Marcy Power Cage System is a durable, multi-use workout machine that gives you the ability to exercise in the comfort of your home or the office. Get to strengthening and toning the muscles in your body with the pull-up bar, weight trolley, abdominal crunch station, and the dips bar. Durability and stability are one of the main features of this cage system, so intense workouts are no problem. 
Pulleys 
The high and low pulleys are made for intense upper and lower body exercises. Core trainings are great with cable pulleys, targeting all muscles. 
Pull-up Station 
The pull-up station has multiple hand grip positions that allow a multitude of pull up exercises. These are perfect for upper body exercises and strengthening the shoulders. 
Leg Anchors 
The leg anchors are heavy duty for total leg development. High-quality foam is used, and the vinyl covering is double stitched to ensure durability. 
Dip Bars 
The dip bars are specially made for high-intensity tricep and chest development training. The bars are covered in foam for comfort. 
Dual Upper and Lower Pulley Cables 
The Marcy Cage System SM-3551 has a single pulley trolley that can be used with the upper or lower pulley for a wide variety of workouts. 
Multi-grip Pull-Up Bar 
The multi-grip pull-up bar allows you to do pull-ups and chin-ups. Pull-ups and chin-ups target several different muscles in your arms, back, and chest. Change up your grip to target a wider range of muscles. 
Sit-Up Station 
Use the Sit-up station to easily do sit-ups without having someone to hold your legs down. 
Adjustable Bar Catches - Squats 
The Marcy Cage System includes adjustable bar catches that can be used at the front of the unit. Use the catches with an Olympic bar for squats and a bench for presses. Squats are great for targeting your quadriceps and glutes.
